GNU m4 1.4 (required for autoconf)

autoconf 2.13 or autoconf 2.5x

automake 1.6 (currently, no other version/subversion will work: the
              setup script invokes automake-1.6)

libtool 1.3.4 (libtool 1.2 will *not* work)

It helps to have GNU gcc and GNU ld installed on the system, too.


